These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, pakistani, thai, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, frog, bird
1. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the colombian##1
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the thai##3
4. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
5. the nigerian is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
7. the pakistani is somewhere between the colombian and the owner of the lizard##7
8. the pakistani and the owner of the bird have the same parity positions##9
9. the thai and the owner of the pony have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | pakistani | thai     | nigerian |
| Pet           | frog   | bird     | lizard | pony  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, fanta, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, gardening, puzzles, writing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is writing and the person drinking mirinda have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
4. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
5. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
6. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite     | fanta    | water | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | photography | gardening | puzzles      | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, iced-tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, tomato, zucchini
1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
2. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the person eating cucumber##8
8. the person drinking water and the person eating cucumber have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | water    | iced-tea   | 7up    | mirinda  |
| Food       | cucumber | zucchini | cranberry | tomato |

