.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, librarian, mechanic, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, classical, folk, jazz
1. the fan house is the librarian##1
2. the fan classical is on the right of the fan folk##1
3. the fan classical is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
4. the fan jazz is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
5. the fan classical is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the scientist and the fan jazz have the same parity positions##9
7. the mechanic is on the left or right of the doctor##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | scientist | mechanic | doctor  | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | folk             | classical          | jazz | house    |

