.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, disco, r&b
4 different pets are kept: mouse, goat, turtle, hamster
1. the fan disco is not the owner of the turtle##6
2. the owner of the mouse and the fan house have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the goat and the fan indie have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fan r&b##1
6. the fan indie is not the owner of the goat##6
7. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the fan house##1
9. the owner of the hamster is not the fan r&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | house | disco | r&b  | indie |
| Pet           | goat   | mouse     | turtle | hamster      |

