1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
4. the spanish and the person watching family movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching martial-arts movies and the spanish have different parity positions##9
6. the japanese is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
8. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the chinese##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | epic | family | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | chinese        | japanese    | spanish   | turkish |

