2. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is badminton##2
3. the person who's sport is volleyball and the fan folk have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan folk is not to the right of the fan gospel##8
6. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
7. the fan folk is somewhere to the right of the fan electronic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | d&b | folk         | gospel     |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | volleyball  | badminton | weightlifting |

