4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the owner of the rat##6
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku and the owner of the dog have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
