.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, cherry, lime, plum
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, quad-bike, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
2. the person eating plum and the person driving the motorbike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
4. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
5. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person driving the motorbike##7
6. the person eating plum is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | lime | garlic   | cherry | plum |
| Transport   | quad-bike   | boat | skateboard    | motorbike      |

