.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, spinach, pumpkin, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, russian, egyptian, thai
1. the person eating avocado is not the thai##6
2. the thai is not to the right of the pakistani##8
3. the person eating pumpkin is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
4. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
5. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
6. the thai is on the far left##1
7. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
8. the person eating mango is the russian##1
9. the person eating avocado and the pakistani have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | spinach   | avocado    | pumpkin | mango    |
| Nationality   | thai | pakistani | egyptian   | russian |

