.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, 7up, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, musical, coffeesy, superhero
1. the person watching horror movies is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
2. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching coffeesy movies##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person watching horror movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching coffeesy movies and the person drinking 7up have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | coffee  | 7up  | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | coffeesy | superhero | horror      |

