.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, electronic, gospel, folk
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan gospel have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 3. the fan indie is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking tea##7
 4. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan gospel is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk and the fan electronic have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
 9. the fan folk is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan indie##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea  | almond-milk | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | folk | gospel     | indie | electronic     |

