.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, sprite, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, video-games, skydiving, dancing
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 6. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the person drinking mirinda and the person who's hobby is video-games have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 9. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is video-games have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | sprite        | mirinda   | iced-tea      |
| Hobby      | dancing | skydiving | video-games | cooking |

 